Compiling LFTP from github source
=================================

 * Make sure compile tools are installed
 * Install dependencies: `sudo apt-get install gnulib gnutls-bin libgnutls28-dev ncurses-dev`
 * Create configuration files`./autogen.sh`
 * if it fails with error:

    configure: creating ./config.status
    config.status: error: cannot find input file: `Makefile.in'

    try `libtoolize`, then again `./autogen.sh`

 * Compile: `make`
 * Executable now at: `./src/lftp --version`

In case of errors, search for error message within this repository: https://github.com/lavv17/lftp
There may be issue reports providing a solution.
